response.overview: Seua Chanee Gayng: Freshy is a 45 minute comedy starring Mankalasut Akalavut as Cheetah, Goy Arachaporn Pokinpakorn as Oil and Reonchaidee Pathompong as Tum. The series premiered on Tue Aug 14, 2018 on and EP08 (S01E08) last aired on Tue Oct 09, 2018.
